No,<br>
<br>
Once it enrages, it will not enrage again even if healed.<br>
<br>
Note, I have had a pet enrage twice a couple times.  Each time the pet had been suspended and a second one cast, then reused the suspended pet and it indeed enraged again.  Might be a bug or the stored pet resets when you cast a new one.<br>
<br>
