<br>
Note: didn't include spells / weapon procs. Pet was buffed with BOV, Velocity, SoV and FoS (I always ask for those buffs, seems to make the pet perform better). 2 Fist of Ixiblat and a Muzzle were it's gear (no belt yet).<br>
<br>
Note2: a flurry3 / crit3 aa'd warrior in my guild was parsed at 100 dps on the same mobs with a Windblade; from the front as the tank.<br>
<br>
These were real-life parsings with the rogue having a 2nd pc and giving results right after the fight so people were really making an effort to maximize dps (pet 99% of the time behind the mob). <p>Arch Convoker Rhand Drago'Magica<br>
